snippet.title: Vantage Short Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Final Short Trailer for Vantage as I am getting ready for Release!
Enjoy!
(There is also a longer version of the trailer here that desribes many more features of the game! https://youtu.be/b5dHvL7_hnc )

The game is now available on Steam if you want to know more about the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/342910/Vantage_Primitive_Survival_Game/
